60
00:04:25,518 --> 00:04:28,479
yang seharusnya tersenyum di sisi kalian.

61
00:04:29,397 --> 00:04:30,815
Mereka perlu tahu itu.

62
00:04:32,859 --> 00:04:35,194
Bukankah kau bagian dari mereka?

63
00:04:35,278 --> 00:04:36,821
Begini, nyatanya,

64
00:04:37,530 --> 00:04:39,824
