67
00:04:53,004 --> 00:04:54,380
tapi pestanya dibatalkan

68
00:04:56,132 --> 00:04:58,050
karena kubilang aku sibuk.

69
00:04:59,427 --> 00:05:01,471
Andai saja kami makan bersama hari itu,

70
