103
00:07:42,506 --> 00:07:44,467
Aku benar-benar melihatnya!

104
00:07:44,550 --> 00:07:45,718
Dal-geon,

105
00:07:46,135 --> 00:07:47,887
apa kau sudah hilang akal?

106
00:07:47,970 --> 00:07:49,639
Aku tidak gila.

107
00:07:49,722 --> 00:07:51,349
Pikiranku jernih!

108
00:07:52,141 --> 00:07:54,060
Aku mengejarnya...

109
00:07:55,519 --> 00:07:57,271
Ini membuatku gila.

110
00:07:57,355 --> 00:07:58,522
Jadi...

111
