Mungkin sebaiknya aku tak di sini.

124
00:08:37,728 --> 00:08:38,562
Tunggu!

125
00:08:39,605 --> 00:08:42,817
Ingat pria yang kuminta
kau hentikan di bandara?

126
00:08:43,401 --> 00:08:44,235
Apa?

127
00:08:45,403 --> 00:08:47,363
